{"tid":1325882,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"蘋果或將取消3D Touch，可以取消，但價格不能降!","createTime":"2019-07-17T04:25:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-19T02:06:43.000Z","uid":141060,"like":4,"dislike":69,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"06c19b6c02ad743f45d23be945b44d3cb38d29dd","tid":1325882,"uid":141060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T04:25:19.000Z","msg":"蘋果或將取消3D Touch原因曝光：用的人少，花錢不值<br />\n 2019-07-17 09:7<br />\n<br />\n月17日消息 據PhoneArena消息，從去年開始就出現了蘋果將在2019年逐步放棄iPhone上的3D Touch功能。 按照知情人士的說法，蘋果取消3D Touch的原因在於很大一部分用戶不使用甚至不了解（有的壓根不知道有）3D Touch這個功能，因此蘋果公司認為不值得繼續在壓感應顯示面板上花錢 。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n 此前，Digitimes報導稱蘋果將從所有iPhone 11型號中移除3D Touch功能，並在其供應鏈中引入新的OLED顯示器製造商京東方。  Digitimes的報告引用了觸控模塊製造商TPK和GIS的消息來源，這是蘋果的主要供應商。 這些製造商最終將減少每台設備的投入，因為新款iPhone的觸控模塊製造起來更簡單，並且元件成本更低。"},{"pid":"f1c5dea12f7047f04c459b971871a9a265afa6d1","tid":1325882,"uid":109923,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T04:41:00.000Z","msg":"支那Mon<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"563421edef859e8d299069358c057d41a35d4666","tid":1325882,"uid":61954,"like":32,"dislike":2,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T04:47:53.000Z","msg":"功能可以少<br />\n錢唔可以少"},{"pid":"f4888085eb9bef1c1aace3105ae03cf1aad3bea3","tid":1325882,"uid":36820,"like":19,"dislike":14,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T04:55:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />apple fans又少樣野打飛機， 唔係好好用ga咩"},{"pid":"1c17f7d0131a50c08b887ef655409047bc63dff6","tid":1325882,"uid":60434,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T04:56:27.000Z","msg":"Ip8有制好撚爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4810d67ac92c82de38aacd5963363edbd24a5d7","tid":1325882,"uid":258746,"like":19,"dislike":3,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T04:58:00.000Z","msg":"我用緊6仔，但我已經感受到3D Touch會係幾咁好用"},{"pid":"aa72bb374e0b800ad5369d232e72ba6604782a76","tid":1325882,"uid":